text: Holzbach is a river of Rhineland-Palatinate, Germany. It is a left tributary of the Elbbach in Gemünden. ==See also== *List of rivers of Rhineland- Palatinate ==References== Category:Rivers of Rhineland-Palatinate Category:Rivers of the Westerwald Category:Rivers of Germany
title: Holzbach (Elbbach, Gemünden)
